    {
      "id": "1904750c-f3ba-8046-8873-ef4c925038ea",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Online learning is often presential learning done remotely, which hinders the ability to deliver on the promise of personalized learning, often leading to lower retention. CSU-Global attempts to mitigate this. Thus, this online HEI started designing multiple learning pathways for their learners. ",
